                    <li>Designed and implemented Django-based compliance review automation workflow, significantly reducing regulatory review time.</li>
                    <li>Independently integrated tax calculation module supporting automatic tax rate calculation based on user location, covering 200+ test scenarios.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
